# Boids Simulation Project Reminder

## Project Overview
- Project Name: Boids Simulation
- Development Environment: Windows + VSCode (Because of toolchain，seems not that easy to setup a profiler for vscode?)
- Goals: 
1. High Performance (Large Scale)
2. Rapid Development
3. ImGui Parameter Adjustment
4. Interesting Visual Effects
5. Scalability and smart design

## Tech Stack
- Programming Language: C++20
- Graphics API: OpenGL 3.3+
- Window Management: GLFW
- OpenGL Loader: GLAD
- UI Framework: Dear ImGui
- Build System: CMake

